# anneal-dev: run-state history (.anneal-dev/runs/) is TRACKED — the accumulated
# run record (foundation.md). Only the local run-gate override flag is ignored: a
# per-developer momentary bypass; committing it would re-arm on every checkout.
.anneal-dev/allow-adhoc-kernel-edit

# Python bytecode cache (e.g. from importing hooks/ during testing)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
